## API Documentation

### OpenAPI Specification

```yaml
openapi: 3.1.0
info:
  title: ANUBIS Chat API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: Solana-native AI chat platform API

paths:
  /api/chat:
    post:
      summary: Send chat message
      operationId: sendMessage
      security:
        - bearerAuth: []
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                message:
                  type: string
                  description: User's chat message
                includeRAG:
                  type: boolean
                  default: true
                model:
                  type: string
                  enum: [claude-3.5, gpt-4o, deepseek]
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Streaming response
          content:
            text/event-stream:
              schema:
                type: string
```

